
Rivet
=====

* rivet is a mini PHP framework intended to speed development.


Features
--------

* regex based URLs using callback-style closures for views
* [Twig](http://github.com/fabpot/Twig) templates. Django templates in PHP. Pimp.


Requirements
------------

* PHP 5.3

Example (index.php)
-------

    <?php
		require_once('rivet/Rivet.php');
		
		// Homepage
		$rivet->route('%^/$%', function($request){
			echo 'Welcome to the rivet homepage!';
		});
		
		// Hello thar! :D
		$rivet->route('%^/hello-world/$%', function($request){
			echo 'Hello World';
		});
		
		// URL params matching & Template usage
		$rivet->route('%^/work/([\w-]+)/([\d]+)/$%', function($request, $foo, $bar){
			return new Template('some_template_file.html', array(
				'foo' => $foo,
				'bar' => $bar
			));
		});
		
		
		echo $rivet->dispatch();
